    <meta
      name='description'
      content=`Learn how to effortlessly book your Pollachi farmstay online. Follow our 5-step guide for a hassle-free reservation process. Secure your rural retreat today!`
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <section class='h-max max-w-[100vw] overflow-x-hidden relative'>
