      </div>
      <NavBarMOB />
      <section
        class='h-max w-screen max-w-[100vw] min-[1590px]:max-w-[99.2vw] overflow-x-hidden font-popins'
      >
        <div
          class='h-max w-full pt-[28vh] flex flex-col px-[4vw] gap-[2.4vh] min-[990px]:gap-[4vh] bg-gradient-to-b from-[#552535]'
        >
          <h1
            class='text-[4.2vh] w-[90%] min-[990px]:w-[60%] min-[990px]:tracking-[0vw] min-[990px]:leading-[7.8vh] min-[990px]:text-[3.2vw] leading-[5.8vh] tracking-[.1vw] text-left text-[#fff]'
          >
            Unlock Your Pollachi Paradise: 5 Lightning-Fast Steps to Book Down
            to Earth Farmstay Now!
          </h1>
          <p
            class='text-[2.8vh] w-[90%] leading-[4.6vh] font-[500] text-[#000] min-[990px]:w-[60%] min-[990px]:text-left'
          >
            Are you craving a slice of rural bliss in the heart of Tamil Nadu?
            Look no further than <a
              class='text-[#552535] font-[600] tracking-[-.1vw] min-[990px]:tracking-[0vw]'
              href='/'>Down to Earth Farmstay by Laksem</a
            > in Pollachi! This guide will walk you through the seamless process
            of securing your perfect getaway. In just five quick steps, you'll be
            on your way to experiencing the authentic charm of Pollachi's countryside.
            Ready to make your dream vacation a reality? Let's dive in!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='h-max w-full flex flex-col gap-[4vh] px-[4vw] pt-[4vh]'>
          <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh] min-[990px]:w-[60%]'>
            Nestled in the lush landscapes of Pollachi, Down to Earth Farmstay
            by Laksem offers an unparalleled escape from the hustle and bustle
            of city life. With its promise of tranquility, organic living, and
            genuine rural experiences, it's no wonder that more and more
            travelers are seeking out this hidden gem. But how do you go about
            booking your stay at this slice of paradise?
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- STEP 1 -->
        <div
          class='h-max w-full flex flex-col gap-[2vh] px-[4vw] pt-[4vh] min-[990px]:w-[60%]'
        >
          <h2
            class='text-[3.2vh] font-[500] tracking-[-.1vw] min-[990px]:tracking-[0vw]'
          >
            Don't Worry – We've Simplified The Process Into Five Easy Steps That
            Will Have You Ready To Go In No Time!
          </h2>
          <div class='h-max w-full flex flex-col gap-[4vh] pt-[2vh]'>
            <h3 class='text-[2.8vh] font-[600]'>
              Step 1: Reach Out via WhatsApp
            </h3>
            <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
              In Today's fast-paced Digital world, Down to Earth Farmstay keeps
              things refreshingly simple. The first step to your rural retreat
              is as easy as sending a message on WhatsApp. Here's what you need
              to do:
            </p>
            <ol class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
              <li>- Save the farmstay's contact number: +91 9894648555</li>
              <li>- Open WhatsApp and start a new chat with this number</li>
              <li>
                - Send a friendly message expressing your interest in booking a
                stay
              </li>
            </ol>
            <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
              <em
                >Pro tip: Include your preferred dates and the number of guests
                in your initial message to speed up the process.
              </em>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- STEP 2 -->
        <div
          class='h-max w-full flex flex-col gap-[2vh] px-[4vw] pt-[4vh] min-[990px]:w-[60%]'
        >
          <h3 class='text-[2.8vh] font-[600]'>
            Step 2: Receive Your Personalized Quote
          </h3>
          <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
            Once you've sent your inquiry, the team at Down to Earth Farmstay
            will promptly respond with a personalized quote. This quote will
            typically include:
          </p>
          <ol class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
            <li>- The nightly rate for your stay</li>
            <li>
              - Any special packages or offers available during your chosen
              dates
            </li>
            <li>
              - Additional information about amenities and experiences included
              in your stay
            </li>
          </ol>
          <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
            Remember, rates may vary depending on the season and availability,
            so it's always a good idea to inquire about multiple date options if
            your schedule is flexible.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- STEP 3 -->
        <div
          class='h-max w-full flex flex-col gap-[2vh] px-[4vw] pt-[4vh] min-[990px]:w-[60%]'
        >
          <h3 class='text-[2.8vh] font-[600]'>
            Step 3: Review and Confirm Your Booking Details
          </h3>
          <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
            After receiving your quote, take a moment to carefully review all
            the details. This is the perfect time to ask any questions you might
            have about your stay. Some common queries include:
          </p>
          <ul class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
            <li>- What's the check-in and check-out time?</li>
            <li>- Are meals included in the rate?</li>
            <li>- What activities are available on the farm?</li>
            <li>- Is transportation from nearby cities available?</li>
          </ul>
          <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
            Don't hesitate to seek clarification – the Down to Earth team is
            there to ensure your stay is perfect from start to finish.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- STEP 4 -->
        <div
          class='h-max w-full flex flex-col gap-[2vh] px-[4vw] pt-[4vh] min-[990px]:w-[60%]'
        >
          <h3 class='text-[2.8vh] font-[600]'>
            Step 4: Make Your Advance Payment
          </h3>
          <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
            Once you're satisfied with all the details, it's time to secure your
            booking with an advance payment. The farmstay will provide you with
            their preferred payment method, which may include:
          </p><ul class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
            <li>- Bank transfer</li>
            <li>- Online payment gateway</li>
            <li>- UPI payment</li>
          </ul>
          <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh]'>
            Always ensure you're using secure payment methods and keep a record
            of your transaction for future reference.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- STEP 5 -->
        <div
          class='h-max w-full flex flex-col gap-[2vh] py-[4vh] px-[2vw] min-[990px]:w-[60%]'
        >
          <h3 class='text-[2.8vh] font-[600] px-[2vw]'>
            Step 5: Receive Your Booking Confirmation
          </h3>
          <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh] px-[2vw]'>
            After your advance payment is processed, you'll receive an official
            booking confirmation. This is your golden ticket to paradise! The
            confirmation will typically include:
          </p>
          <ul class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh] px-[2vw]'>
            <li>- Your booking dates</li>
            <li>- The total amount paid and any remaining balance</li>
            <li>
              - Important information about your stay, such as what to bring and
              how to reach the farmstay
            </li>
          </ul>
          <!-- IMAGE -->
          <div
            class='min-[990px]:hidden h-max w-full border-[1.5px] rounded-md pt-[2svh] px-[2vw] border-[#999] overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-between justify-between gap-[2svh]'
          >
            <Image
              alt='Rooms at Deluxe Cottage at Down To Earth Farmstay by Laksem, Pollachi'
              class='rounded-sm h-[32svh] object-cover'
              decoding='async'
              loading='lazy'
              src={Img}
            />
            <div class='h-max w-full flex flex-col items-start gap-[.4vh]'>
              <p class='text-[#333] text-[2.8vh]'>Deluxe Cottages</p>
              <p class='text-[#666] text-[2vh]'></p>
              Down To Earth Farmstay by Laksem
            </div>
            <a
              class='w-max block text-center pb-[1vh] text-blue-800 border-[#999] text-[2vh] font-[500] underline underline-offset-[.5vh]'
              href='/'>View Details</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <div
        class='h-max w-full px-[4vw] bg-gradient-to-t from-[#F5EFDA] pb-[4vh] min-[990px]:pb-[8vh]'
      >
        <p class='text-[2.4vh] leading-[4.2vh] min-[990px]:w-[60%]'>
          Booking your stay at Down to Earth Farmstay by Laksem in Pollachi is a
          breeze with this five-step process. From your initial WhatsApp message
          to receiving your confirmation, you're just moments away from
          embarking on an unforgettable rural adventure. <br /><br /> The simplicity
          of the booking process reflects the farmstay's commitment to providing
          a genuine, hassle-free experience from start to finish.
          <br />
          <br /> So why wait? Your perfect Pollachi getaway is just a WhatsApp message
          away. Reach out to Down to Earth Farmstay today and take the first step
          towards creating memories that will last a lifetime. <br /><br /> Remember,
          paradise is not just a place – it's an experience waiting to be booked!
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
